"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1932392-Carlos-Alcaraz-net-worth-olympics-novak-djokovic\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Carlos Alcarazmay have been beaten by old foeNovak Djokovicin the men's singles final of theOlympics, but he will receive a decent reward for hissilver medal.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Alcaraz ran out victorious when the two met at the finals ofWimbledonthis summer, beating the tennis great 6-2, 6-2, 7-6 onCentre Courtafter an impressive tournament.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 161, \"end\": 168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.450831597051446e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Djokovic had his revenge at this summer'sOlympics in Paris, beating the Spaniard 7-6, 7-6 to add a gold medal to his 24 career Grand Slam wins.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 333, \"end\": 341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1961328926334293e-21, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0239224557012254e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And while Alcaraz will no doubt be unhappy to take home silver instead of gold, he will receive a decent amount from his country for a respectable second-place finish.\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 487, \"end\": 494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.450831597051446e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's because theSpanish Olympic Comittee (COE)award \\u20ac48,000 (\\u00a341,206) to silver medallists in individual competitions.\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old would have been \\u20ac94,000 (\\u00a380,683) better off had he been successful in defeating Djokovic, while a third-place finish still would have generously handed him \\u20ac30,000 (\\u00a325,751) from the singles competition.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 864, \"end\": 872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1961328926334293e-21, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, the Olympic prize money that Alcaraz will receive for his efforts is a far cry from the money he bagged from hisWimbledonwin earlier this summer.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1029, \"end\": 1036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.450831597051446e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The south-west London Grand Slam paid out \\u00a32.7million to its victor, while Djokovic was awarded \\u00a31.4million for his second-place finish.\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1961328926334293e-21, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is reported that Alcaraz has already racked up a staggering net worth of around $15million (\\u00a311.7million) through his tennis endeavours and lucrative sponsorship deals.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.450831597051446e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The youngster has 15ATP Tour titlesand fourGrand Slamsto his name in the form of a2022 US Openwin,2023 and 2024 Wimbledonvictories, and aFrench Opensuccess earlier this year.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999761159666483, \"rank\": 2.1847577894913874e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In terms of sponsorships, meanwhile, Alcaraz has worked with the likes of Nike, Babolat, Rolex, ElPozo, BMW and Calvin Klein to name a few.\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.450831597051446e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolex\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rolex\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolex\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolex\"}, {\"begin\": 1736, \"end\": 1739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMW\", \"score\": 0.9998956464856458, \"rank\": 0.00010427734528777989, \"text\": \"BMW\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMW\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMW\"}, {\"begin\": 1744, \"end\": 1756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calvin_Klein\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.530269872498625e-30, \"text\": \"Calvin Klein\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q3501317\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calvin_Klein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calvin_Klein\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spanish sensation's road to the Olympic final was fairly straightforward, save a potentially tricky semi-final affair.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1776, \"end\": 1783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9346615171941944, \"rank\": 0.06776050859882392, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Alcaraz took on Hady Habib in his opening game, before battling with Tallon Griekspoor in the second round.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2054, \"end\": 2061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.450831597051446e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 2070, \"end\": 2080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hady_Habib\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hady Habib\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hady_Habib\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hady_Habib\"}, {\"begin\": 2123, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tallon_Griekspoor\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tallon Griekspoor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tallon_Griekspoor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tallon_Griekspoor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A victory over Roman Safiullin saw him advance to a quarter final with Team USA's Tommy Paul, winning 6-3, 7-6 to make it to the semis against Felix Auger Aliassime.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2233, \"end\": 2241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998000908108, \"rank\": 1.9444274480384204e-07, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2244, \"end\": 2254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.164506165801898e-19, \"text\": \"Tommy Paul\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\"}, {\"begin\": 2305, \"end\": 2326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/F\\u00e9lix_Auger-Aliassime\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Felix Auger Aliassime\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/F\\u00e9lix_Auger-Aliassime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/F\\u00e9lix_Auger-Aliassime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He triumphed 6-1, 6-1 against the Canadian, before giving it his all against Djokovic in the final.\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2363, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9995220094560658, \"rank\": 0.00047817892624248733, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 2406, \"end\": 2414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1961328926334293e-21, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately it wasn't his day on the clay at Roland-Garros, with Djokovic reigning supreme and denying the youngster of his third landmark achievement of the year after the French Open and Wimbledon.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2496, \"end\": 2504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1961328926334293e-21, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alcaraz had to cut short his on-court interview with Alex Corretja after the loss, struggling to get his words out through the tears of coming so close to Olympic greatness.\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2632, \"end\": 2639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.450831597051446e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 2685, \"end\": 2698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c0lex_Corretja\", \"score\": 0.9999998300823025, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Corretja\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c0lex_Corretja\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c0lex_Corretja\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was consoled by the journalist, who put his arm around Alcaraz before giving him space and continuing his analysis of the match solo.\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2864, \"end\": 2871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.450831597051446e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alcaraz would later return to say: \\\"I gave everything,\\\" before conceding he was bettered by his opponent.\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 3051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2946, \"end\": 2953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.450831597051446e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"It's painful to lose the way I lost this match,\\\" going on: \\\"I had my chances to probably be up in the match.\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not take it.\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3192, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Novak was playing great.\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He deserves this.\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the tough moments he increased his level.\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3468, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"He played unbelievable shots... an unbelievable game.\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a bit disappointed but honestly I will leave the court with my head really really high.\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fighting for Spain was everything to me.\", \"from\": 3674, \"to\": 3714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3687, \"end\": 3692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999997765667353, \"rank\": 2.2295803549175694e-07, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am proud with the way I played today.\\\"\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3894, \"end\": 3907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0700032426654971e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"h